Our resolvers are relatively straightforward. Weve set our message resolvers to return in descending order by date created, so the most recent messages will return first.

Notice weve also included a resolver for `Date` because it's a custom scalar. Instead of creating our own resolver, Ive imported someones excellent [`GraphQLDate`](https://www.npmjs.com/package/graphql-date) package.

