[}]: #

The Object returned from `optimisticResponse` is what the data should look like from our server when the mutation succeeds. We need to specify the `__typename` for all  values in our optimistic response just like our server would. Even though we dont know all values for all fields, we know enough to populate the ones that will show up in the UI, like the text, user, and message creation time. This will essentially be a placeholder until the server responds.

